# Model config: Devstral-Small-2-24B-Instruct-2512 (Q6_K, dense coder)
#
# Rationale:
#   - Mistral recommends temp 0.15 for Devstral: coding/agentic work wants near-deterministic
#     output, not creative sampling. top-p 1.0 leaves the low temp in control.
#   - Agentic tool-caller: pairs with --jinja (launcher default) for tool use.

: "${MODEL:=Devstral-Small-2-24B/Devstral-Small-2-24B-Instruct-2512-Q6_K.gguf}"

LLAMA_ARGS+=(--temp 0.15 --top-p 1.0)
